nodes.text: Denise Ream was Visual Effects Executive Producer for Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith.

She appeared in Revenge of the Sith as a cameo, portraying Onara Kuat, in Romeo Treblanc's private viewing box at the Galaxies Opera House. Aidan Hennessy wrote her backstory through the What's The Story? feature on Hyperspace.
